**Player** | Werewolves Revamped
__Basics__
A Player is a participant in a Werewolves Revamped game.
__Details__
Each Player consists out of five elements:
• Person: The person behind the Player and their username.
• Ingame Identity: The nickname and emoji representing the the Player ingame.
• Primary Role: The Player's *role*. Each Player has exactly one role from the townsfolk, werewolf, unaligned or solo category.
• Extra Roles: Additional *roles* of the *extra* category.
• Player Attributes: Player's may receive *player attributes* throughout the game.

A Player's person and ingame identity may be replaced with another person and ingame identity in case a substitution happens. All substitutions are announced.
